properties.select_statement:
WITH CTE AS (
    SELECT *,
        CASE
            WHEN REGEXP_CONTAINS(NAMA_CUSTOMER, r'AND/OR|TBK|QQ|CMC|KANWIL|DIVISI|PROPINSI|PROVINSI|CAPEM|CABANG PEMBANTU|CABANG|CAB|AREA|CONSUMER|MBU|MMU|COMMERCIAL|RETAIL|CBG|BRANCH|-|/') THEN
                REGEXP_EXTRACT(NAMA_CUSTOMER, r'(AND/OR|TBK|QQ|CMC|KANWIL|DIVISI|PROPINSI|PROVINSI|CAPEM|CABANG PEMBANTU|CABANG|CAB|AREA|CONSUMER|MBU|MMU|COMMERCIAL|RETAIL|CBG|BRANCH|-|/)')
            ELSE
                NAMA_CUSTOMER  -- Return the full name if no match is found
        END AS delimiter,
         -- Extract the part of the name *before* the delimiter
        CASE
            WHEN REGEXP_CONTAINS(NAMA_CUSTOMER, r'AND/OR|TBK|QQ|CMC|KANWIL|DIVISI|PROPINSI|PROVINSI|CAPEM|CABANG PEMBANTU|CABANG|CAB|AREA|CONSUMER|MBU|MMU|COMMERCIAL|RETAIL|CBG|BRANCH|-|/') THEN
                TRIM(SUBSTR(NAMA_CUSTOMER, 1, REGEXP_INSTR(NAMA_CUSTOMER, r'AND/OR|TBK|QQ|CMC|KANWIL|DIVISI|PROPINSI|PROVINSI|CAPEM|CABANG PEMBANTU|CABANG|CAB|AREA|CONSUMER|MBU|MMU|COMMERCIAL|RETAIL|CBG|BRANCH|-|/') - 1))
            ELSE
                NAMA_CUSTOMER
        END AS NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX
    FROM `eternal-synapse-401311.POC.Customer`
where nama_kategori <> 'PERSEORANGAN'
    
)

SELECT 
    KODE_NASABAH,
    CTE.NAMA_CUSTOMER,
    CASE 
        -- WHEN NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX LIKE '%BRI%' THEN 'BANK RAKYAT INDONESIA' 
        -- WHEN NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX LIKE '%BCA%' THEN 'BANK CENTRAL ASIA' 
        -- WHEN NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX LIKE '%BNI%' THEN 'BANK NEGARA INDONESIA' 
        -- WHEN NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX LIKE '%BTN%' THEN 'BANK TABUNGAN NEGARA' 
        -- WHEN NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX LIKE '%PLN%' THEN 'PERUSAHAAN LISTRIK NEGARA' 
        WHEN UPPER(NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX) like '%BNI%'  THEN 'Bank Negara Indonesia'
        WHEN UPPER(NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX) like '%BRI%'  THEN 'Bank Rakyat Indonesia'
        WHEN UPPER(NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX) like '%BCA%'  THEN 'Bank Central Asia'
        WHEN UPPER(NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX) like '%BTN%'  THEN 'Bank Tabungan Negara'
        WHEN UPPER(NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX) like '%BTPN%' THEN 'Bank Tabungan Pensiunan Nasional'
        WHEN UPPER(NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX) LIKE '%JAMKRINDO%' THEN 'Jaminan Kredit Indonesia'
        WHEN UPPER(NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX) LIKE '%ASKRINDO%' THEN 'Asuransi Kredit Indonesia'
        WHEN UPPER(NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX) LIKE '%JASINDO%' THEN 'Asuransi Jasa Indonesia'
        WHEN UPPER(NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX) LIKE '%REASURANSI INDONESIA%' THEN 'Reasuransi Indonesia Utama'
        WHEN UPPER(NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX) LIKE '%ASEI%' THEN 'Asuransi Asei Indonesia'
        WHEN UPPER(NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX) LIKE '%JIWASRAYA%' THEN 'Asuransi Jiwasraya'
        WHEN UPPER(NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX) LIKE '%PLN%' THEN 'Perusahaan Listrik Negara'
        WHEN UPPER(NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX) LIKE '%BPD%' THEN 'Bank Pembangunan Daerah'
        WHEN UPPER(NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX) LIKE '%BPR%' THEN 'Bank Perkreditan Rakyat'
        ELSE NAMA_CUSTOMER_FIX  -- Use the fixed name here
    END AS NAMA_CUSTOMER_NEW,
    NAMA_KATEGORI,
    INTERCO_CD
FROM CTE
ORDER BY NAMA_CUSTOMER;
